0.1.name: wordpress/collroll
0.1.description: Collapsing Blogroll allows you to put your built-in blogroll on a page or in a post. Just put [collroll] in the place where it should appear. The categories can be collapsed. No extra database table is needed. You can add new links as you did it in the past.
